{"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/UIKit\/UIView\/environment"},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:17ViewEnvironmentUI0aB11PropagatingPAAE11environment0aB0AEVvp::SYNTHESIZED::c:objc(cs)UIView","roleHeading":"Instance Property","modules":[{"name":"ViewEnvironmentUI"}],"extendedModule":"ViewEnvironmentUI","symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"environment"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15ViewEnvironmentAAV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ViewEnvironment"}],"title":"environment"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/viewenvironmentui\/uikit\/uiview\/environment"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"code":"ViewEnvironment","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" that is flowing through the propagation hierarchy.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI","doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/UIKit","doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/UIKit\/UIView"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"environment","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15ViewEnvironmentAAV","text":"ViewEnvironment","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you’d like to provide overrides for the environment as it flows through a node, you should conform to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"ViewEnvironmentObserving","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and provide those overrides in "},{"code":"customize(environment:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". E.g.:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["func customize(environment: inout ViewEnvironment) {","    environment.traits.mode = .dark","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, this property gets the environment by recursively walking to the root of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"propagation path, and applying customizations on the way back down. The invalidation path may be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"interrupted if a node has set it’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"environmentAncestor"},{"type":"text","text":" to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":", even if there is a node"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"which specifies this node as an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"environmentDescendant"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you’d like to update the return value of this variable and have those changes propagated through the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"propagation hierarchy, conform to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewEnvironmentObserving"},{"type":"text","text":" and call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setNeedsEnvironmentUpdate()"},{"type":"text","text":" and wait"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for the system to call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"apply(context:)"},{"type":"text","text":" when appropriate (e.g. on the next layout pass for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIViewController"},{"type":"text","text":"\/"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIView"},{"type":"text","text":" subclasses)."}]},{"type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIViewController"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIView"},{"type":"text","text":" conformers "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"must","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"applyEnvironmentIfNeeded()"},{"type":"text","text":" in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"viewWillLayoutSubviews()"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"layoutSubviews()"},{"type":"text","text":" respectively."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Important","style":"important"}]}],"references":{"doc://ViewEnvironmentUI/documentation/ViewEnvironmentUI/UIKit":{"kind":"symbol","title":"UIKit","identifier":"doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/UIKit","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/viewenvironmentui\/uikit","role":"collection","abstract":[]},"doc://ViewEnvironmentUI/documentation/ViewEnvironmentUI":{"abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI","kind":"symbol","title":"ViewEnvironmentUI","role":"collection","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/viewenvironmentui"},"doc://ViewEnvironmentUI/documentation/ViewEnvironmentUI/UIKit/UIView/environment":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"environment","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"environment","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ViewEnvironment","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15ViewEnvironmentAAV"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"code":"ViewEnvironment","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" that is flowing through the propagation hierarchy.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/viewenvironmentui\/uikit\/uiview\/environment","identifier":"doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/UIKit\/UIView\/environment","role":"symbol"},"doc://ViewEnvironmentUI/documentation/ViewEnvironmentUI/UIKit/UIView":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/v